text: Kapos ako sa Day 2 test cases. I don't check the ranges between BX25-BX50, BX75-BX99 that well. It only works with 100% accuracy if the poison is on barrels BX01-BX025. I can just add more barrels though, otherwise, it's accurate to within 50 barrels.    I'd modify but am lazy.  =/
